Corporate Partners Program


MISSIONThe ICS Corporate Partners Program promotes the exchange of the most advanced information in the field between university researchers and their corporate counterparts, and provides access to the abilities and interests of UC Irvine’s students through exclusive recruiting and networking opportunities.
OBJECTIVES

Excellent customer service/individualized attention
Streamlined communication
Priority access to students and faculty within your specific area(s) of interest



Contact Jason King, Senior Associate Director of Corporate Relations, at Jason.King@uci.edu or (949) 824-3088.




